"title": "8829: superstition",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8829",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Misplaced credulity concerning the supernatural, which leads to irrational fear, misdirected reverence, false religion and magic, and which brings God's judgment. Scripture warns against and condemns such things.</p>\n<h2>Superstition causing irrational fear</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:2\">JER 10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:20-Job15:24\">JOB 15:20–15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:11\">JOB 18:11</a></p>\n<h3>Fear of Jesus Christ or his disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:26-Matt14:27\">MAT 14:26–14:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:49-Mark6:50\">MRK 6:49–6:50</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:2\">MAT 14:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:14\">MRK 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:13\">ACT 5:13</a></p>\n<h3>Fear of other gods</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:23\">1KI 20:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:28\">1KI 18:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:28\">1KI 20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:23\">ACT 17:23</a></p>\n<h2>Misunderstanding God's work</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:18-Acts8:19\">ACT 8:18–8:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:36-Luke24:37\">LUK 24:36–24:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:15\">ACT 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:13\">ACT 19:13</a> <em>invoking the name of Jesus Christ for exorcism as though it were a magic formula</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:3-Acts28:4\">ACT 28:3–28:4</a></p>\n<h2>Superstition leading to misdirected reverence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:11-Acts14:13\">ACT 14:11–14:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:5-Acts28:6\">ACT 28:5–28:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:8-Rev22:9\">REV 22:8–22:9</a></p>\n<h2>False religion</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:6-Judg10:7\">JDG 10:6–10:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:3-1Sam7:4\">1SA 7:3–7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:33\">1KI 13:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:15-1Kgs14:16\">1KI 14:15–14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:22-1Kgs14:24\">1KI 14:22–14:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:2-2Chr28:4\">2CH 28:2–28:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:3-2Kgs16:4\">2KI 16:3–16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:14\">JER 9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:17-Jer44:18\">JER 44:17–44:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:2\">HOS 11:2</a></p>\n<h2>Unhelpful speculations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3-1Tim1:4\">1TI 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:2-Isa65:3\">ISA 65:2–65:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:17-Isa66:18\">ISA 66:17–66:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:2\">EZK 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:17\">EZK 13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3-1Tim6:4\">1TI 6:3–6:4</a></p>\n<h2>The true demonic source of superstition</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20-Rev9:21\">REV 9:20–9:21</a></p>",
